summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easement over portions of H.E. Orr Park Addition; Rose Addition No. 2; plat of Sunset Estates; Addition to the Town of Seattle, commonly known as A.A. Denny's Fifth Addition to the City of Seattle; Boulevard Place Addition to the City of Seattle; Northwest Quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Southeast quarter of Section 9, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Lake Forest Park Third Addition; and East Park Addition to the City of Seattle.
